description: Here's Fig, waking up in bed with someone she'd much rather not wake up with. This, of course, leads to an unpleasant and bloody confrontation. What happens when one of the House of Mystery residents tries to kill another? Featuring an urban fairy tale illustrated by Sam Kieth (THE MAXX).
name: Management Part 3 of 4; Sucked In

volume.name: Mad's Maddest Artist Don Martin Drops 13 Stories!
Mad's Doldwaze Artiest Don Martin Laat Alles Vallen!

description:
Get caught up on all the latest action going on in the Marvel Universe! First, it’s an action-packed Ms. Marvel story featuring Captain America and Jessica Jones. Then, he has near limitless power — now he must do all he can to bring punishment to the wicked, help to the oppressed, and justice for all! Exploding from the pages of Annihilation, it’s Nova! Also, follow the adventures of Danny Rand in a history-spanning kung-fu epic that will shatter every perception of what it means to be the Immortal Iron Fist! Next, the final confrontation between Ghost Rider and Lucifer begins! Plus, the X-Men’s past becomes the present as Xavier fights the greatest battle of his life. With his mind hanging in the balance, one false move can cause irreversible damage.

Collects:

  • Ghost Rider #14 (2006)
  • The Immortal Iron Fist #1 (2007)
  • Ms. Marvel #1 (2006)
  • Nova #1 (2007)
  • X-Men: Legacy #208 (2008)
name: Volume 1

description: Spider-Man and his amazing friends are there for the birth of a brand new hero!! Who is he? What is his name? Here’s a hint: It’s a name that will make you burst out in applause!! He’s set to be major player in the Ultimate Universe, so be there as hotshot creators BRIAN MICHAEL BENDIS (ULTIMATE SPIDER-MAN) and TAKESHI MIYAZAWA (RUNAWAYS) bring you his big debut!
name: Crossroads Part 2

description: It’s the action-packed and twist-filled finale of THE SINNERS as TRACY LAWLESS finds himself trapped between hardened killers who want to torture and kill him, and a tough Military Investigator who wants to bring him back to the Army in chains. All the intrigue you’ve come to expect from Criminal, plus more exclusive back-up features and interviews.
name: The Sinners, Part 5

description: When school budget cuts hit, Archie is forced to home school via computer. Will he be late for class in his own home? Then, a snow day brings out the adventurous side of Archie and the warm side of his wardrobe! Plus, other new and classic stories, puzzles, pin-ups, and more!
name: The Ultra Cool School

description: First appearance of RIPCORD! The latest candidate for G.I. JOE status may already be dead! Meet Wallace Weems, a soldier everybody calls RIPCORD. Lost in a forbidding jungle, Ripcord has one mission: SURVIVE! And if he doesn't outwit, outfight, and outlast the terrorists hunting him, thousands more might die!
name: R.I.P.CORD Part 1: You Say Jump...

description: After a brief, demonic waylay, the Ghoul and Detective Klimpt finally come face-to-face with the horror they have sought. What began as a Hollywood rumor takes a twisted turn for the worst and the recently teamed-up monster and cop find themselves in a nightmare of glitz, glamour and guts! Also, part three of the prose Ghoul adventure “My Ghoul” also concludes as Wrightson, Niles and IDW dole out a generous dose of horrors.

Love may be blind, but it is certainly not deaf. Which is why the Music Box is able to so thoroughly complicate the life of a cheating husband and his mistress. From the mind of Jennifer Love Hewitt comes another thriller as written by Scott Lobdell and illustrated by Casey Maloney (Gene Simmons Zipper).
name: Wishes

description:
The A-Team are back! Before you see their return on the big-screen, thrill to this special mission told in comic book form only! After a successful-but harrowing-completion to a mission in icy Alaska, Hannibal and the team are up for some much-needed leave in sunny San Diego to attend the wedding of a high-ranking U.S. official’s daughter.

But when threats are made against the event, the A-Team is forced to quit their vacation and go undercover to foil what might be a terrorist plot.

It’s a beatdown of literally monumental proportions when the Hulk and the Wrecking Crew wage war in our nation’s capitol! And when the dust settles, what of Washington DC will remain unsmashed?! All this plus rocking extras giving YOU the goods on WORLD WAR HULKS - the upcoming Hulk mega-event!!
name: Let The Battle Begin!; Gammaragnarok!

description:
1. The Blackhawks Vs. Blackbeard (Blackhawk)
 
2. Will Bragg (by Paul Gustavson)
 
3. Dogtag (by Bart Tumey)
 
4. Torchy (by Bill Ward)
 
5. Poodle McDoodle (gag page)
 
6. Ezra (by Harry Sahle)
 
7. Blackhawk (text story)
 
8. Choo Choo (by Gill Fox)
name: The Blackhawks Vs. Blackbeard

description:
Scooby Doo - The Ancient Astronaut - 11 pages

Scooby Doo - Curse Of The Wishing Well - 14 pages
name: The Ancient Astronaut

description: "Complete in this issue"
name: Sparkle Plenty T.V. Mystery

volume.name: Dick Tracy Comics: Special Edition for Motorola, Inc.

description: With Agent Brand imprisoned, all hell breaks loose! Norman Osborn and the Dark Avengers set out to destroy a group peaceful aliens while a war-like race is about to unleash the most intelligent and dangerous being in the universe! Now Brand herself is about to walk in a trap that could spell the end of everything she’s worked for…and her life!

Want to know what it takes to break into Marvel Comics like these guys? Then look no further than this two-part book which is a must-have for anyone wanting to be a Comic Book Breakout Star! After traveling the globe and meeting scores of talented illustrators, intrepid writer, editor and talent manager C.B. Cebulski is giving twelve rising star artists the opportunity to do their breakout work at Marvel Comics! But not only will BREAKING INTO COMICS THE MARVEL WAY showcase the work of these up-and-comers, C.B. will also provide an insider’s commentary on how these artists got their work seen and what it was that landed them the gig. And with step-by-step submission information and a sample Marvel Comics script, these books are MUST HAVES for anyone interested in doing their breakout work and breaking into the comics industry!

Features Include:

Street Level

Let it Out

Icarus's Wings

Let Sleeping Devils Lie

It's Not Lupus!

Modern Love
name: Street Level; Let it Out; Icarus's Wings; Let Sleeping Devils Lie; It's Not Lupus!; Modern Love

volume.name: Breaking Into Comics The Marvel Way!

description: "Pro-Life," part 4! With only three more issues until this acclaimed series reaches its shocking conclusion, the tragedies that Mayor Hundred warned about in the very first issue finally come to pass.
name: Pro-Life, Part Four

description:
The Kree are one of the Fantastic Four's oldest enemies; the Shi'ar, one of the X-Men's oldest allies. But it's the Avengers who are caught in the middle when the two alien races wage a war to re-write Marvel's map of the universe! As two-legged WMDs land on Earth, the Avengers end up as alien invaders on wartorn worlds of wonder, both as a unit and individually! Featuring the Imperial Guard! Starforce! Deathbird! Thor vs. Gladiator! Super heroes from three galaxies and more clash in the first half of the story that shook the team to its foundations!

Reprints Captain America #398-399, Avengers West Coast #80-81, Quasar #32-33, Wonder Man #7-8, Avengers #345-346, Iron Man #278 and Thor #445.
name: Volume 1

first_appearance_objects.name: Iron Man Space Armor Mk. II

object_credits.name: Iron Man Space Armor Mk. II

description:
One galaxy's heroes are another's villains, and two galaxies' worth of them collide head-on - with the Avengers in the middle of a war whose repercussions will haunt them for years! The events that split and shook Earth's Mightiest Heroes to their foundations end here, and intergalactic boundaries aren't the only lines being drawn! Plus: The tri-galaxy war devastates Earth far more literally when we see 'What If the Avengers Lost Operation: Galactic Storm?'!

Reprints Iron Man #279, Thor #446, Captain America #400-401, Avengers West Coast #82, Quasar #34-35, Wonder Man #9, Avengers #347, What If? #55-56.
name: Volume 2

description: Once upon a time, in a world of super heroes and villains, there lived a team of animals that saved the universe…and no one knew it. These creatures asked not for fortune or fame, merely to help the humans that pet them. But a new threat to the world has arisen, which only they know of, that could change everything…and kill one of them. Join CHRIS ELIOPOULOS, IG GUARA, and CHRIS SOTOMAYOR for an epic tale of adventure, courage…and sacrifice.

volume.name: Lockjaw and the Pet Avengers Unleashed

description: With his best pal gone, Deadpool continues his trek through time and space, spreading friendship and mercenary whoop-&*$ throughout the cosmos. Featuring titanic team-ups with Wolverine, Captain America, Doctor Strange, Brother Voodoo, Ka-Zar and the Fantastic...Eight?! And in the unforgettable series finale, the dreaded Venom Symbiote has multiplied, and made some new friends of the prehistoric variety, giving the Merc with a Mouth his final opportunity to prove himself the ultimate hero - or the ultimate villain! Guest-starring Spider-Man! The Fantastic Four! The Mighty Avengers! And of course, those lovable goons from Agency X!
name: VS. The Marvel Universe

description:
The Fantastic Four! X-Factor! The X-Men! The Avengers! What threat could menace all four major Marvel teams of the 1980s? Can you say...the Devil? Mephisto wants super-hero souls, and he's out to collect them all! With their worst nightmares AND their wildest dreams at his command, he's not getting cast out of THIS fight! How can he lose...when it's HIS series?    
 
 Reprints Mephisto Vs. #1-4.
name: Mephisto vs...

description:
Meet Spider-Man - hero to the people, champion of the weak and oppressed...and World Wrestling Alliance Championship Titleholder?! Peter Parker has it all: respect, fame and the adoration of all. But he also has a deep, destructive secret that he keeps from the world and from his family - one that could well unravel the reality he knows!

Reprints Spider-Man: House of M #1-5.
name: TPB

description: FINAL ISSUE! Who remembers Gary Gaunt? Considered a monster during World War II, he was secretly dropped behind German lines so his terrible “Jekyll and Hyde” transformations would disrupt the German war effort. Gaunt…forgotten by society, has been able to control his hideous transformations for over 60 years…but when his special serum is stolen, Nova and the Avengers find themselves at ground zero with the strangest man/ monster of them all!

Walker's past has come to bite him right in his ##$! big time and it's going to take a @#$@#$ and a $@#$@ to get him out of the !@$#@#$@$@$@. It's another potty mouth chapter in the award winning cops-meets-capes epic saga from the creators of Secret Invasion and The Mice Templar.
name: Z (Part 3)

description: The once-in-a-lifetime crossover that brought two super-teams together and rocked the comics world is at last available in trade paperback! Own the entire 4-issue co-publishing event between DC and Marvel and written by Kurt Busiek (TRINITY, Marvels) with stunning art by George Pérez (Final Crisis: Legion of Three Worlds, Avengers). This collection also features introductions by original Avengers writer/editor Stan Lee and Justice League of America editor Julius Schwartz.
name: JLA / Avengers

description: What would Superman do if his secret identity as Clark Kent was discovered by one of his greatest foes? Could he protect his friends and loved ones? How radically would his life change? These questions had figured in Superman's worst nightmares. When the deadly villain Conduit makes those nightmares a chilling reality, there remains but one answer... In order for Superman and all those close to him to live... Clark Kent must die!
name: Superman: The Death of Clark Kent

volume.name: Superman: The Death of Clark Kent

description: Check out an ALL-NEW tale featuring the characters from the upcoming MARVEL SUPER HERO SQUAD SHOW!
name: When Slurks The Slime!; Thor And Iron Man in Reflections!; Captain America And Flacon: Together Again For The First Time!

description:
Europe, 1945: Captain America leads a mission to destroy the Nazis' missile program...and The Phantom Reporter wants in! An untold tale from Marvel's Golden Age featuring the forgotten heroes who would go on to become "The Twelve"!

Chapter Titles

  • Part One: Super-Dooper Supermen!
  • Part Two: War Time Blues
  • Part Three: Plans and Executions
name: Into the Fatherland!

description: Mr. X is back for a rematch and revenge on the only man who’s ever beaten him: Wolverine! Find out everything you never knew about one of the most dangerous psychopaths in the Marvel Universe. The first time these two met, Wolverine barely escaped with his life, and this time… well, one thing’s for sure, you’ll never see the end coming but you’ll love how you got there!
name: Unfinished Business

description: Mysteries continue to mount regarding the “mutant burnout” phenomena and the shadowy organization known only as the “Consortium”. After ferreting out a complex network of double-agents infiltrating S.H.I.E.L.D., Nick Fury is left with only one choice: to infiltrate the Consortium himself. With a team of X-Men behind him, the Consortium is about to get hit by Hurricane Nicholas! Don’t miss a minute of the heart-pounding action from comics icon CHRIS CLAREMONT!
name: The Ties That Bind

description: Dark arts have come to the fore and Dhruv has been checkmated once! An ambitious student manages to find a rare book on voodoo! A spate of crimes using this ancient form- of black magic suddenly plagues Rajnagar. Dhruv is forced to give the criminals a lending hand in a heist! Why did agree to follow the diktat of the criminals? Who is the mysterious man who forces Dhruv to become an accomplice in his crime? How will Dhruv counter this ancient form of black magic? Will he be able to turn the tables and bring the criminal to justice? Watch out for the exciting Rita Rampuri who is skilled in using knives! Join Dhruv in his battle against dark arts exclusively on Raj comics.
name: Woo Doo

description: A mysterious man saves the residents of Rajnagar from a terrorist attack. To the utter surprise of the people he manages to survive the explosion. The terrorists wishing to settle scores attack the old man. When Dhruv tries to intervene, the old man opens fire at Dhruv! Dhruv is perplexed with this action and he is faced with a new dilemma when he unravels the mystery of the old man. The old man causes wide scale destruction in Rajnagar when Dhruv refuses to accede to the request of the old man! What is so unusual about his request? Will Dhruv succeed in saving Rajnagar from destruction? A mysterious man, a bunch of scrupulous terrorist and Dhruv battle it out at Rajnagar. Read an exciting adventure of Dhruv, available exclusively on Raj Comics. Grab a copy today!
name: Mujhe Maut Chahiye(I want Death)

description: Dhruv can be easily identified in his costume. A growing fan club wants to emulate their super star! Dhruv's costume becomes the new fashion statement among the kids of Rajnagar! But an old foe is training predators to attack Dhruv. This jeopardizes the security of several innocent kids as the predator targets people who are wearing the trendy costume! A lion attacks Shweta who was sporting Dhruv's costume but she manages to blind the lion! Dhruv is a marked man and he must reach his persecutor before innocent kids get killed! Dhruv believes that he is on a hot trail of predators. But is he being induced to fall in a well laid trap! Why cannot he communicate to the predators? Will he be able to tame a savage gorilla in combat? Who is this adversary who loathes Dhruv enough to attempt to kill Dhruv in such macabre fashion? Dhruv's past has returned to haunt him! Read a thriller high on adrenalin exclusively on Raj Comics.
name: Bahri Maut

description: A jumbo jet has been hijacked! Dhruv's mother and Shweta were among its passengers. They are held hostage by a cruel dictator Witler who rules the mech men. He wants the humans to surrender to the rule of the Mech-men a race of mechanized men and women. Now it's up to Dhruv to under take a risky mission to the future (25,000 AD) and secure the safe release of the hostages! Dhruv needs to summon his wit and resourcefulness to win this battle! Can Dhruv become a savior of the oppressed? Time travel, hostages, a cruel dictator and a futuristic battlefield; makes an exciting plot to read. This timeless adventure is exclusively available on Raj Comics.
name: Udantashtari ke Bandhak

description: A sworn enemy of Dhruv is out to seek revenge! He helps an ex-convict Bhujang who is on death row, to escape from the prison. He bestows Bhujang with Herculean strength and sends him on a mission to destroy Dhruv. Every member of commando force switches his allegiance to the enemy camp once they have been kidnapped by Bhujang! What is the mystery of the revolt of commando force? You shall be shocked beyond your wildest imagination to watch Dhruv robbing a jewelers shop! Later Dhruv finds him self facing an execution squad compromising of his near and dear ones! Will the enemy reveal his identity to Dhruv before eliminating him? Discover the mystery of betrayal and enjoy a great climax only on a Raj Comics publication.
name: Ek Din Ki Maut

description: The Army of Darkness has been set free once more by an unfortunate Reader of the Necronomicon Ex-Mortis! With the help of Ash, Darkman fights to save the City and bring back Julie!
name: Darkman vs Army of Darkness

description: A nuclear explosion has rocked the shores of Rajnagar! Grand master Robo a feared international terrorist is elated with the success of the explosion, as he could blackmail countries to cave in to his demands! But unfortunately the shores of Rajnagar were littered with dead fishes killed due to the nuclear radiation! Dhruv alerts the police about the incident and radiation is confirmed! A fire breathing monster attacks a bus which was en-route to the atomic power plant at Rajnagar! Even Chandika is unable to stop the monster. Dhruv and Peter visit the blast site and discover Swarn Nagri, a city of gold. They have to beat a retreat when Peter gets injured in an attack by Robo's henchmen! The existence of Swarn Nagri and its inhabitants which was a well guarded secret has been exposed as Grand Master Robo has also come to know of its existence! Chandika manages to make friends with Natasha a student of journalism by saving her life who returns the favor by helping the commando force! Discover the close guarded secret of Swarn Nagri and its inhabitants? Will they be friends of foes to the human race! What is the mystery behind the monster breathing out fire? Will Robo succeed in is evil designs! It is easily the greatest adventure involving Dhruv! The epitome of good and evil face each other in person for the first time! Also introducing Dhananjay who will become a crucial ally of Dhruv in the days to come! Catch this racy adventure with an excellent from of story telling exclusively on Raj Comics!
name: Grand Master Robo

description: You simply cannot believe your eyes when the harmless plants turn into predators! And neither could Dhruv when he was accompanying his friend Shekhar, who worked as a forest guard! But a mysterious tribal who could talk to plants and trees and make them obey his commands, incited the trees to execute the poachers. This savage tribesman is out to seek revenge against timber merchant who is felling the trees mercilessly! Dhruv is really impressed with the tribal and his ability to talk to the plants! But can Dhruv teach the savage a thing or two about law? Will the savage kill the timber merchant or fall in a trap laid by the devilish timber merchant! The tribesman commands the loyalty of the entire flora on this planet! Now he teaches them to retaliate against the timber mafia! Will good sense prevail?
name: Vinaash Ke Vriksh

description: Dhruv is a last moment replacement for team India in racing tournament of international sports meet at Rajnagar. A formidable foe, which prefers to be addressed as Champion Killer attacks Dhruv as he mistook him for world Champion Galileo! He also issues a threat to kill three other world Champions during the sports meet. Dhruv manages to escape the bid on his life with his resourcefulness and Champion Killer acknowledges Dhruv as a true champion! Dhruv and Champion killer face each other twice but Champion killer manages to give him the slip on both the occasions! Dhruv has earned the wrath of Champion Killer due to his constant intervention! Will Dhruv stop this determined killer from crippling the athletes for the rest of their lives? Is there a hint of mystery surrounding the four world champions whom the Champion killer wishes to cripple for life? Find it out in an enthralling adventure exclusively at Raj Comics!
name: Champion Killer

description: The world Champions leave for Bonn in a bid to trap Champion Killer at their own back yard! Champion Killer mange's to escape Dhruv for the third time in a row! He has taken Natasha as a captive! The sports institute at Bonn where the world champs used to train, holds the key to the riddle of Champion Killer. Dhruv reaches Bonn to investigate and comes to know about Kara, the man who unravels the mystery around Champion Killer! With Dhruv in hot pursuit will Champion Killer manage to cripple the world champs? Will Dhruv manage to unmask the true identity of Champion Killer before it is too late? Why does Champion killer seek to cripple the four world champs? Dhruv has finally met his match in Champion Killer who is athletic, skilled in combat and has a sharp mind. Can Dhruv finally out maneuver his opponent? Read a fast paced adventure exclusively on Raj Comics.
name: Akhiri Daon(Last Move)

description: Two precious inventions of Professor Kale have been stolen from his office! One of his assistants has been brutally murdered, while another is reported missing! Dhruv clashes with one of the famed villains till date; Dhwani Raj! Dhwani Raj has the ability to transform the harmless sound waves into a lethal form causing wide scale destruction! He has unleashed a pet monster which is all energy and no mass which goes on the rampage in Rajnagar! Dhwani Raj has challenged Dhruv for a duel else he would wreck the town! The clock is ticking and Dhruv is racing against time to thwart Dhwani Raj executing his threat! Sheweta's gadgets come in really handy in combating Dhwani Raj! Will the true identity of Dhwani Raj be finally revealed to us? Can Dhruv stop this menacing criminal from achieving his ultimate goal! Catch a racy adventure of Dhruv exclusively on Raj Comics!
name: Aawaj Ki Tabahi(Destruction of sound)

description: A dangerous criminal, Vaman escapes from the famed Narka jail using his electronic toys. Natasha and Chandika who were present in the jail at that moment were unable to contain this master criminal! Vaman seeks the four puppets of Dhruv which were distributed as prizes in a shooting competition and is ready to travel any length to obtain these puppets! What makes these puppets so special? Dhruv tries his level best to get Vaman arrested but Vaman foils his attempt with his resourcefulness! Two agents of unfriendly nations have been spotted by the police but they manage to give them the slip! Are these incidents correlated? Vaman is the most resourceful and adorable villain Dhruv has ever encountered! Can the team trap Vaman who always has an ace up his sleeves? Read an engrossing battle between the commando force and Vaman, exclusively on Raj Comics!
name: Khooni Khilone

description: Two universes have to fight to save their realms. The Biggest Stars from DC and Marvel have to fight each other. If one side loses, their Universe will be destroyed!!
name: DC vs. Marvel
Koww Koww
Bheriya
Inspector Steel
Ayee Shakti
Super Indian
Danga
Yoddha
Khofnaak Khel
Main Hoon Bheriya

description:
Wade Wilson and Nathan Summers - Marvel's mightiest mutant mercs - are back, and this time they're stuck with each other! Can two grown men armed to the teeth with deadly genetic weaponry live together without driving each other crazy?! Action, adventure, black humor, black-ops, face-changing viruses, gratuitous France-bashing and lots of gunfire mark the return of two of Marvel's fan-favorite anti-heroes! Plus: this edition comes complete with all letters pages, never before reprinted!    
 
Reprints Cable and Deadpool #1-18.
name: Book One

first_appearance_locations.name: Jean Grey School for Higher Learning

location_credits.name: Jean Grey School for Higher Learning

description: After the shattering events of issue #49, we start to pick up the pieces with "M.I.A.", a four-part story taking Matty to a remote and desolate section of the city. With no phone, no computer and no contact at all with any of his friends, what exactly is he doing there, and why?
name: M.I.A. Part 1

description:
The end is near! Eastern Europe is frozen solid in the grip of a sudden ice age. A tidal wave of biblical proportions mercilessly sweeps through New York City. Millions have been killed, and countless more injured or displaced — among them members of the X-Men and Fantastic Four. And Magneto is to blame. In the wake of this unimaginable catastrophe, is it a time to repent? Or is it a time for revenge? See Ultimatum through the eyes of two of the world's greatest teams — or what's left of them, at least!

Collects Ultimate X-Men #98-100, Ultimate Fantastic Four #58-60.

The unthinkable has happened as the X-Men find themselves reeling from the devastating events of Ultimatum. A band of humans have stolen Sentinel technology and attacked Xavier's mansion - killing any mutant they see! With the X-Men locked in battle with Magneto, can anyone save these students? Their greatest hope might rest in the hands of their worst enemy as the Weapon X program returns! Also, Ultimatum has hit the planet hard and the Baxter Building was ground zero. Johnny is still missing. Dr. Storm is dead. And Reed has taken off to parts unknown. Sue's life hangs in the balance and rests in the hands of untested pilot Ben Grimm, a.k.a. The Thing, and Dr. Arthur Molekevic, now better known as the megalamonical Mole Man.
name: HC/TPB
